00:13:27,723 --> 00:13:31,292
Dog, plane, house, dog, plane...

245
00:13:41,988 --> 00:13:44,872
OK, Iz, are you gonna
tell me what you saw?

246
00:13:51,547 --> 00:13:53,014
Show her the cards.

