00:13:54,117 --> 00:13:55,332
What's this?

248
00:13:59,689 --> 00:14:02,089
Dog. Can you say "dog"?

249
00:14:06,763 --> 00:14:10,231
- What's my name?
- Just stick to the cards,
Meredith.

250
00:14:14,671 --> 00:14:16,437
Meredith.

251
00:14:16,539 --> 00:14:18,956
You know my name.
You can say my name.

252
00:14:23,629 --> 00:14:27,381
- This is what I was afraid of.
