253
00:14:29,635 --> 00:14:32,820
Iz, you don't have to speak.
Just nod your head for me

254
00:14:32,922 --> 00:14:35,689
if you know who Alex Karev is.

255
00:14:49,488 --> 00:14:51,917
The test impaired your
memory to such a degree

256
00:14:51,941 --> 00:14:54,792
that I strongly recommend
you don't have the surgery.

257
00:14:54,894 --> 00:14:57,006
Izzie, it was the
worst-case scenario.

258
00:14:57,030 --> 00:14:59,898
- It has nothing to do with the surgery.
- - We don't know that.

259
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:02,077
I do know that not
operating is every bit as risky,

260
00:15:02,101 --> 00:15:06,137
if not more so.
But it's up to you.

261
00:15:08,158 --> 00:15:11,925
- What do you think?
